    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Required Fields Present?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.type }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Work in Batches · ②→ Abort — Malformed Input",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
